For this assignment, you are requested to make a RMD file in which you are comparing the differentially methylated CpGs (DMCs) between EPP and TC populations of the mangrove rivulus liver.
You have to answer the following question: 
- what is the range of the total number of CpGs among all samples ?
- what is the coverage value of the percentile 99.9% when taking all CpGs from sample TC liver 2 into account ?
- what is the number of CpGs common in the 6 samples ?
- How many CpG have you found differentially methylated between the 2 populations ? Justify the different chosen parameters in methylKit (don’t use covariate).
- What is the highest qvalue found ?
- what is the percentage of significant CpG located in promoter region ?
- how many unique genes have you identified ?
- choose one CpG and explain why your finding is interesting (including its annotation) ?

